items.checkin_comment: A greener, more bitter hazy.  Really well-done. Pineapple, pomelo, and lychee followed by pine, frsh wet grass for a little greeness, bright fruity florals, and maybe a touch of chalk, but not offensively so.  A good benchmark for hazy IPAs.
